fe-Is-Strange-Double-Exposure-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Life-Is-Strange-Double-Exposure-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Life-Is-Strange-Double-Exposure-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/deck-nine-games">Deck Nine</a>已经确认了<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/life-is-strange">《奇异人生》</a></em>系列的新作， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/life-is-strange-double-exposure"><em>《双重曝光》</em></a>将于今年晚些时候发布。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/life-is-strange-true-colors-needed-an-emotional-and-honest-soundtrack-and-julia-stone-is-the-perfect-fit-3034910">《奇异人生：本色》需要情感丰富且诚实的配乐——而朱莉娅·斯通是完美的选择</a></strong></li></ul><p>被称为“全新谋杀之谜”的<em>《奇异人生：双重曝光》</em>将让玩家与第一部<em>《奇异人生》</em>游戏的主角马克斯·考菲尔德重聚。</p><p>在预告片中，我们看到麦克斯已经长大了，并且这次经历了不同的力量。她现在不再能够倒带时间，而是能够体验两条几乎相同的平行时间线。</p><p> “当马克斯·考菲尔德发现她的朋友萨菲死在雪地里时，她撕开了通往平行时间线的道路。在这里，萨菲还活着——而且仍然处于危险之中！凭借她在两条时间线之间切换的新能力，麦克斯可以解决并阻止同一起谋杀案，” <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1874000/Life_is_Strange_Double_Exposure/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>列表中写道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="奇异人生：双重曝光 – 公布预告片 (PEGI)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ciia3eBFnb8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>麦克斯在原版<em>《奇异人生》</em>和前传<em>《暴风雨前夕》</em>中出现过，但在最近的<em>《奇异人生》</em>中只被顺便提及。</p><p> <em>《奇异人生：双重曝光》</em>将于 10 月 29 日在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X/S</a>上发布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch">Nintendo Switch</a>版本也已确定。</p><p> <em>《奇异人生：双重曝光》</em>在昨天（6 月 9 日）的 Xbox 游戏展示会上宣布。此次展示还确认了新的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/doom">《毁灭战士》</a></em>游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/doom-the-dark-ages-revealed-at-xbox-games-showcase-2024-3763931"><em>《黑暗时代》</em></a>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/gears-of-war">《战争机器》</a></em>前传游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/gears-of-war-e-day-announced-at-xbox-games-showcase-2024-3763940"><em>《E-Day</em></a> 》。<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>还通过宣传预告片分享了对即将推出的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/call-of-duty-black-ops-6">《使命召唤：黑色行动 6》</a></em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/heres-the-campaign-gameplay-trailer-for-call-of-duty-black-ops-6-3763936">深入了解</a>，并宣布了新的成人游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/iggy-pop-joy-division-smashing-pumpkins-and-more-to-soundtrack-new-mixtape-game-3763996"><em>Mixtape</em></a> ，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/devo">Devo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roxy-music">Roxy Music</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smashing-pumpkins">The Smashing Pumpkins</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lush">Lush</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/siouxsie-and-the-banshees">Siouxsie 和Banshees</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joy-division">Joy Division</a> 。</p><p>今年早些时候，九号甲板被迫发表声明，否认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/life-is-stranger-developer-deck-nine-denies-reports-of-racism-and-harassment-3614813">工作室存在种族主义和骚扰的报道</a>。</p><p>在其他消息中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/shenmue">《莎木》</a></em>的粉丝们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/shenmue-fans-rent-times-square-billboard-to-campaign-for-new-game-3763612">在纽约时代广场租了一块广告牌</a>，向<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sega">世嘉</a>施压，要求其制作第四款<em>《莎木》</em>游戏。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/life-is-strange-double-exposure-brings-back-original-protagonist-with-new-powers-3764048">《奇异人生：双重曝光》的</a>帖子首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上，该帖子以新的力量带回了原来的主角。</p> ;
